pro_course_detail.description:
Interesting conversational practice is the best way to gain your confidence in conversation! In this lesson, we will discuss a wide range of topics to improve your spoken Russian :) 
We will train your conversational skills through various activities:
- discussion on any topics;
- spontaneous chat;
- storytelling;
- role-play (situations in a restaurant, in a hotel etc);
This will definitely help you build your vocabulary, boost your confidence and reduce your accent to speak like a native.
*** We will always be able to discuss your wishes on the topic of the conversation together before the lesson. Let me know if you have any preferences and suggestions so that I can make our lesson as effective as possible :) 
Let's break down language barriers easily and naturally! :)

